The paper proposes a new image encryption scheme based on chaos theory, which falls under the category of cryptography (cs.CR). The paper also discusses the use of permutation and diffusion stages, which are common techniques in information theory (cs.IT) and control systems (cs.SY). The paper specifically focuses on image encryption, which is a subfield of multimedia (cs.MM) and computer vision (cs.CV).
